My first venture into creating YouTube videos with nutrition was this video where I got 7 #AAPI Registered Dietitian Nutritionist's to help showcase the foods of Asia. It was fun and a great opportunity to help put some #AAPI on the map. A big thank you to Simon Sum, DCN, RDN, ACSM-CPT, ACSM-EIM, FAND Vandana Sheth, RDN, CDCES, FAND Grace A. Derocha RD, CDCES, MBA Tina Lam MS, RD, LDN, CDCES Jennifer Tao, MS, RDN, CDN, CDCES Ai James, MS, RDN and Andrew Akhaphong, MS, RD, LD #nutrition #eatright #rdchat #culturalfoods #aapiheritagemonth https://lnkd.in/gp2GrJd
